description.text:
This Fancy Esplora case is streamlined for turning your Esplora into an input device.  
I repurposed JoeyC's design so that the whole package would be a lot thinner and require less parts. For example, there are now pegs instead of screw holes, so the Arduino just sits in place.  
And yes, the mustache is required. Just kidding; feel free to replace with your own &quot;flair.&quot;
